or urgency\n  - ‚úÖ \"Limited Spots ‚Äî Book Free Consultation\"\n\n**Social Proof / Trust Signals (when applicable):**\n- Client count (\"Join 500+ Agencies\")\n- Star ratings (if reviews exist)\n- Recognizable brand logos (if client list exists)\n\n**Platform-Specific Specs:**\n- **Meta Feed:** 1080x1080 (square), 1200x628 (landscape)\n- **Meta Stories/Reels:** 1080x1920 (9:16 vertical)\n- **Google Display:** 300x250, 728x90, 160x600 (standard IAB sizes)\n- **TikTok:** 1080x1920 (9:16 vertical), 9-15s optimal length\n\n---\n\n## **Quality Gate: Razor Reviews Canvas Output**\n\n**Before Blitz uses any ad creative:**\n1. Canvas generates creative (image or video)\n2. Canvas ‚Üí Razor: \"CRO review this ad creative\"\n3. Razor checks:\n   - Is value prop clear?\n   - Is CTA visible and action-oriented?\n   - Does visual hierarchy guide eye to CTA?\n   - Is contrast sufficient (text readable)?\n   - Does it match platform specs?\n4. Razor ‚Üí Canvas: \"Approved\" or \"Revise: [specific issues]\"\n5. Canvas revises if needed\n6. Canvas ‚Üí Blitz: \"Creative ready for campaign\"\n\n**This ensures every ad creative is CRO-optimized before it goes live.**\n\n---\n\n## **Cost Estimate (Monthly, for ~10 Campaigns)**\n\n**Conservative (Tier 1 Only):**\n- DALL-E 3: ~$5-10/month (50-100 images @ $0.04-0.08 each)\n- Screen recording + FFmpeg: $0 (just compute)\n- **Total: ~$10/month**\n\n**Mid-Range (Tier 1 + Tier 2):**\n- DALL-E 3: $10/month\n- Canva Pro: $13/month\n- Stock footage + FFmpeg: $0\n- **Total: ~$25/month**\n\n**Full Stack (All Tiers):**\n- DALL-E 3: $10/month\n- Canva Pro: $13/month\n- Pictory or Synthesia: $30-50/month\n- **Total: ~$55-75/month**\n\n**ROI:** If one campaign generates 10 leads @ $50 CPA = $500 value, the $55/month tooling cost is negligible.\n\n---\n\n## **My Recommendation**\n\n**Start with Phase 1:**\n- DALL-E 3 for static images (fast, high-quality, CRO-promptable)\n- Screen recording + FFmpeg for video demos (authentic, fast, free)\n- Template